		"Id": "mechdef_hermes_HER-1O",
		"Name": "Hermes",
		"Details": "The Hermes is a rare chassis in modern times, mostly found in the inventory of the Free Worlds League, but since it was a Star League Defense Force design it can occasionally be found in 'Mech graveyards across the Inner Sphere. And so it was that the Oberon Confederation discovered one such graveyard on one of their planets, Paulus, and set about restoring the design to service. Powered by a 270-rated Prototype XL engine, built with Cobbled-Together Reinforced bones, and clad in stole Ferro-Fibrous armor, the HER-1O is highly advanced for such a limited pirate nation. The weaponry however is relatively mundane. A pair each of Medium Lasers and Slug MGs provide close-up capabilities while a Pepperbox Rifle provides some unexpected ranged punch. The -1O quickly became a favored scout of the Confederation, with pilots getting into fights for the right to drive one of them.",
		"Icon": "uixTxrIcon_hermes"
	},
